title: DDFP 350: Where will Mariota go?
itunes:title: DDFP 350: Where will Mariota go?
description:
Live from Chicago, Shek is joined by Handsome Hank, Bucky Brooks and producer Black Tie to discuss how the quarterbacks will impact the 2015 NFL Draft: Is Marcus Mariota really worth the 2nd overall pick (15:58) and will a team reach for one of the remaining QBs in the 1st round (17:57)? 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
